name: Meeting-grey
tagline: An entry into Bacon Game Jam 09. Theme was "Depth."
body:
### Packages
No packages are currently available.

### Description
This project was made in 48 hours for Bacon Game Jam 09. Meeting Grey is a simplistic 2D platformer that allows swapping between two different depths to progress in the level. More information about Bacon Game Jam 09 can be found [here](https://bacongamejam.org/jams/bacongamejam-09/).
